{"tid":1389421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"令香港警察淪為過街老鼠 (遊客篇)","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:22:53.000Z","uid":36563,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"320c055262e48d68eefd8894eb7967c5a08bac79","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"基於香港警察已經淪為政府政治工具<br />\n我地必需將佢地既暴行宣揚出去！<br />\n<br />\n除左我地係Reddit Twitter做電子文宣之外<br />\n<br />\n我地更應該製作一系列用不同語言 (英，法，德，西班牙，葡萄牙，日，韓 etc.) 製成既紙本文宣<br />\n係機場抵港大堂派比外國遊客<br />\n最好可以同時播下啲紀錄片再加以講解<br />\n<br />\n比佢地知道警察濫權濫暴，會用槍射向平民，暴力對待示威者，勾結黑社會襲擊市民袖手旁觀，仲會打外國人推落地<br />\n<br />\n最後要提醒佢地唔好信任香港警察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成件事既目的係要<span style=\"color: red;\">令遊客知道香港警察既真面目，</span>再等佢地將呢個訊息帶返去比佢地既國家，令到香港警察成為全世界既過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n係香港佢地有中共港共撐腰，<br />\n但出到外國就只係普通人一個<br />\n<br />\n我地要等佢地一世都抬唔起頭<br />\n唔敢再話比人知佢地係警察，為呢份職業為恥！"},{"pid":"661f85a58f04dccfb00395314273157e3958989e","tid":1389421,"uid":126115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"遊乜客 繼續叫其他國家發旅警最實際"},{"pid":"f62bc03d0fa5506ab94a7f1dda38a004b88ddaac","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"661f85a58f04dccfb00395314273157e3958989e","tid":1389421,"uid":126115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"遊乜客 繼續叫其他國家發旅警最實際"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"但外國人會以為香港問題係示威者引起社會混亂<br />\n<br />\n而我係希望向外國人宣傳黑警先係社會動盪根源，同埋喚醒遊客對警察既不信任"},{"pid":"5c2409b6fa36456692fb03960d1462b6ba64425f","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:09:09.000Z","msg":"係呢個時候，我地咩都要去試下<br />\n<br />\n打擊黑警自尊，從心理上攻擊佢地都會好有效"},{"pid":"4b0bb7103dbcdc696ecdaf732580357e7845021b","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"係黑警自己將175年既招牌打爛，我地就幫佢地一把，等佢地名譽掃地"},{"pid":"6cd8697d6ab06e66f53a957b5e211d5f5900e5fd","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"比負皮既果條黑警出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc580ec1bb28ef5f30cfeaea63548263f245172c","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"要敵人從內裡土崩瓦解"},{"pid":"03e81f50387f657e4c3c5d16f19cc2697ce6100f","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"我地可以搞多幾次機場集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2284ed7370fcc71a47d947a3d1bd9dc1075f9bbf","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"逼佢地只可以返大媽區旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac1cb1ec34e7e725a81ad6788754b1c78b12bbc","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bfd8fd27397dd3083e875edeb219185e03b97c","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c0e9dc77fe9127fa502556d603fc2483dcb36176","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"65d9210f6627bae1a1ce6671ff4f90b62085a947","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d0b3ace0a080b3821f61d59a0acbb148ad0692a4","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c8492a3987924e86d4e9a8d13630f38b7fec958d","tid":1389421,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"176c07fc83